1. Run all tests in Pytest

pytest -v -s test_PytestDemo.py

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. Run all tests(from all modules) in a path

pytest -v -s C:\Users\inasahu\PycharmProjects\Python-Selenium\PyTestDemo\

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Run specific test method from a module

pytest -v -s test_PytestDemo.py::test_loginByFaceBook

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4 Running specific Test from Parent window

pytest -v -s \PyTestDemo\test_Pytest\Allure_Reporting_pytest\test_Orange_AllureReporting.py